  "detailed_description": "Welcome to the Arcane Domains!<br><br>This is a short, third person beat-em-up game. Take your mage across the map, rescuing wizards, collecting treasure, and fighting enemies as you work to make the domains safe. Each level takes between 3 - 10 minutes to complete. You have 18 spells available to you at the start of the game, with five additional spells to discover. Summon skeletons, launch fireballs, cast lightning, or whatever else you need in order to save the day.<br><br><u>Cast devastating spells on the lizardmen</u><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/983790/extras/84dececf18ddcd781c0b48ed5464ea0a.avif?t=1552700862\" width=480 height=270 /></span><br><br><u>Visit the vast domains</u><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/983790/extras/98b39d2bb8a4504f8c3ed3ad3fddaf68.avif?t=1552700862\" width=480 height=282 /></span><br><br><u>Use your spellbook</u><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/983790/extras/cacd414c8c66bb99875e46028dce50cd.avif?t=1552700862\" width=480 height=270 /></span><br><br><u>Rescue other wizards to unlock new spells</u><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/983790/extras/c9dae845a4e90db4da094b37f99ac95e.avif?t=1552700862\" width=480 height=270 /></span><br><br><u>Find Treasure to help you on your journey</u><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/983790/extras/41bbb9ef9178bc08f780ff72614d661b.avif?t=1552700862\" width=480 height=310 /></span><br><br><u>Fight four different bosses</u><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/983790/extras/ea53ddd0572c6182487651b8dd5968e9.avif?t=1552700862\" width=480 height=268 /></span><br><br><u>Have a friend help you in split screen co-op</u><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/983790/extras/29ed948b78c78bb73c844933c5958bcc.avif?t=1552700862\" width=480 height=368 /></span><br>Two Controllers are Required for Co-Op",
